{
	"info": {
		"name": "Reservas Salas UAO - API Completa",
		"description": "Colección completa para probar todos los endpoints del sistema de reservas de salas de reuniones por facultad.\n\n## Flujo de Prueba Recomendado\n1. Obtener CSRF Token\n2. Registrar usuario (Docente y/o Secretaria)\n3. Login para obtener session token\n4. Listar Facultades\n5. CRUD de Salas (Secretaria)\n6. Gestión de Recursos (Secretaria)\n7. Crear/Listar/Cancelar Reservas\n\n## Variables\n- `baseUrl`: URL base del servidor (default: http://localhost:3000)\n- `csrfToken`: Token CSRF de NextAuth (se obtiene automáticamente)\n- `sessionToken`: Cookie de sesión (se obtiene automáticamente tras login)",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{ "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "csrfToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "sessionToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "roomId", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "recursoId", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "salaRecursoId", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "reservationId", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "facultadId", "value": "1", "type": "string" }
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "🔐 Auth",
			"description": "Autenticación: registro, login (NextAuth Credentials) y obtención de sesión.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "1. Obtener CSRF Token",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"const data = pm.response.json();",
									"if (data.csrfToken) {",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('csrfToken', data.csrfToken);",
									"    pm.test('CSRF Token obtenido', () => pm.expect(data.csrfToken).to.be.a('string'));",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/csrf", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "csrf"] },
						"description": "Obtiene el token CSRF necesario para las llamadas de NextAuth (login/register). Se guarda automáticamente en la variable `csrfToken`."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "2. Registrar Usuario (Docente)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 201 - Usuario creado', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
									"const data = pm.response.json();",
									"pm.test('Tiene id y rol', () => {",
									"    pm.expect(data).to.have.property('id');",
									"    pm.expect(data).to.have.property('rol');",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Juan Docente\",\n  \"correo\": \"juan.docente@uao.edu.co\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"facultadId\": {{facultadId}}\n}"
						},
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register"] },
						"description": "Registra un nuevo usuario. El rol se asigna automáticamente: SECRETARIA si el correo está en lista_blanca, DOCENTE en caso contrario.\n\nCampos requeridos:\n- nombre (2-100 chars)\n- correo (debe ser @uao.edu.co)\n- password (6-50 chars)\n- facultadId (int, facultad existente)"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "2b. Registrar Usuario (Secretaria)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 201 - Secretaria creada', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
									"const data = pm.response.json();",
									"pm.test('Rol es SECRETARIA', () => pm.expect(data.rol).to.eql('SECRETARIA'));"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Maria Secretaria\",\n  \"correo\": \"maria.secretaria@uao.edu.co\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"facultadId\": {{facultadId}}\n}"
						},
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register"] },
						"description": "Registra una secretaria. IMPORTANTE: El correo debe existir previamente en la tabla `lista_blanca` para que se asigne el rol SECRETARIA."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "3. Login (NextAuth Credentials)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200 - Login exitoso', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
									"// Extraer session token de cookies",
									"const cookies = pm.response.headers.filter(h => h.key === 'set-cookie');",
									"cookies.forEach(cookie => {",
									"    const val = cookie.value;",
									"    if (val.includes('next-auth.session-token')) {",
									"        const token = val.split('next-auth.session-token=')[1].split(';')[0];",
									"        pm.collectionVariables.set('sessionToken', token);",
									"        pm.test('Session token guardado', () => pm.expect(token).to.be.a('string'));",
									"    }",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" }],
						"body": {
							"mode": "urlencoded",
							"urlencoded": [
								{ "key": "csrfToken", "value": "{{csrfToken}}" },
								{ "key": "correo", "value": "maria.secretaria@uao.edu.co" },
								{ "key": "password", "value": "password123" },
								{ "key": "json", "value": "true" }
							]
						},
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/callback/credentials", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "callback", "credentials"] },
						"description": "Login via NextAuth Credentials provider. Envía datos como form-urlencoded.\n\n⚠️ IMPORTANTE: Primero ejecutar 'Obtener CSRF Token' para que csrfToken esté disponible.\n\nEl session token se guarda automáticamente de las cookies de respuesta."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "4. Obtener Sesión Actual",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
									"const data = pm.response.json();",
									"pm.test('Sesión tiene usuario', () => pm.expect(data).to.have.property('user'));"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/session", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "session"] },
						"description": "Verifica la sesión actual del usuario autenticado. Devuelve datos del usuario (id, nombre, correo, rol, facultadId)."
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "🏢 Facultades",
			"description": "Listado de facultades (endpoint público).",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Listar Facultades",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
									"pm.test('Es un array', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.be.an('array'));",
									"const data = pm.response.json();",
									"if (data.length > 0) {",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('facultadId', data[0].id);",
									"    pm.test('Facultad tiene id y nombre', () => {",
									"        pm.expect(data[0]).to.have.property('id');",
									"        pm.expect(data[0]).to.have.property('nombre');",
									"    });",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/faculties", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "faculties"] },
						"description": "Lista todas las facultades activas ordenadas por nombre. No requiere autenticación. Guarda automáticamente el ID de la primera facultad."
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "🏠 Salas",
			"description": "CRUD completo de salas de reunión. Crear/Editar/Cambiar estado requiere rol SECRETARIA.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Listar Salas (por facultad)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
									"pm.test('Es un array', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.be.an('array'));",
									"const data = pm.response.json();",
									"if (data.length > 0) {",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('roomId', data[0].id);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rooms", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "rooms"] },
						"description": "Lista todas las salas de la facultad del usuario autenticado. Requiere auth."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Crear Sala (Secretaria)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 201 - Sala creada', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
									"const data = pm.response.json();",
									"if (data.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('roomId', data.id);",
									"pm.test('Sala tiene nombre y capacidad', () => {",
									"    pm.expect(data).to.have.property('nombre');",
									"    pm.expect(data).to.have.property('capacidad');",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Sala de Reuniones A\",\n  \"ubicacion\": \"Edificio 1, Piso 3\",\n  \"capacidad\": 10\n}"
						},
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rooms", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "rooms"] },
						"description": "Crea una nueva sala. Solo SECRETARIA.\n\nCampos:\n- nombre (requerido, 2-100 chars)\n- ubicacion (opcional, max 200 chars)\n- capacidad (requerido, 2-100)"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Obtener Sala por ID",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
									"pm.test('Sala tiene id', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property('id'));"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/{{roomId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{roomId}}"] },
						"description": "Obtiene una sala específica por su ID."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Editar Sala (Secretaria)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200 - Sala actualizada', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "PUT",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Sala de Reuniones A - Actualizada\",\n  \"ubicacion\": \"Edificio 1, Piso 3, Ala Norte\",\n  \"capacidad\": 15\n}"
						},
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/{{roomId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{roomId}}"] },
						"description": "Edita una sala existente. Solo SECRETARIA. Todos los campos son opcionales."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Deshabilitar Sala (Secretaria)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
									"pm.test('Sala deshabilitada', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().habilitada).to.eql(false));"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "PATCH",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"habilitada\": false\n}"
						},
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/{{roomId}}/status", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{roomId}}", "status"] },
						"description": "Deshabilita una sala. Solo SECRETARIA."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Habilitar Sala (Secretaria)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
									"pm.test('Sala habilitada', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().habilitada).to.eql(true));"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "PATCH",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"habilitada\": true\n}"
						},
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/{{roomId}}/status", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{roomId}}", "status"] },
						"description": "Habilita una sala previamente deshabilitada. Solo SECRETARIA."
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "🖥️ Recursos Tecnológicos",
			"description": "Gestión de recursos tecnológicos y su asignación a salas.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Listar Todos los Recursos",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
									"pm.test('Es un array', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.be.an('array'));",
									"const data = pm.response.json();",
									"if (data.length > 0) pm.collectionVariables.set('recursoId', data[0].id);"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/resources", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "resources"] },
						"description": "Lista todos los recursos tecnológicos disponibles (proyector, pizarra, etc.)."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Listar Recursos de una Sala",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
									"pm.test('Es un array', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.be.an('array'));"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/{{roomId}}/resources", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{roomId}}", "resources"] },
						"description": "Lista los recursos asignados a una sala específica."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Agregar Recurso a Sala (Secretaria)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 201 - Recurso asignado', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
									"const data = pm.response.json();",
									"if (data.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('salaRecursoId', data.id);"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"recursoId\": {{recursoId}}\n}"
						},
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/{{roomId}}/resources", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{roomId}}", "resources"] },
						"description": "Asigna un recurso tecnológico a una sala. Solo SECRETARIA.\n\nCampo requerido:\n- recursoId (int, ID del recurso tecnológico)"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Retirar Recurso de Sala (Secretaria)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200 - Recurso retirado', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
									"pm.test('Mensaje correcto', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().message).to.include('retirado'));"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "DELETE",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/{{roomId}}/resources/{{salaRecursoId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "rooms", "{{roomId}}", "resources", "{{salaRecursoId}}"] },
						"description": "Retira un recurso de una sala. Solo SECRETARIA. El `rid` es el ID de la relación sala_recurso."
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "📅 Reservas",
			"description": "Crear, listar y cancelar reservas. Horario permitido: 7:00 AM - 9:30 PM. No se permiten solapamientos.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Crear Reserva",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 201 - Reserva creada', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
									"const data = pm.response.json();",
									"if (data.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('reservationId', data.id);",
									"pm.test('Estado es CONFIRMADA', () => pm.expect(data.estado).to.eql('CONFIRMADA'));"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"salaId\": {{roomId}},\n  \"fecha\": \"2026-03-25\",\n  \"horaInicio\": \"09:00\",\n  \"horaFin\": \"10:30\",\n  \"motivo\": \"Reunión de coordinación académica\"\n}"
						},
						"url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/reservations", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "reservations"] },
						"description": "Crea una nueva reserva. Cualquier usuario autenticado.\n\nCampos:\n- salaId (requerido, int)\n- fecha (requerido, formato YYYY-MM-DD)\n- horaInicio (requerido, formato HH:MM, >= 07:00)\n- horaFin (requerido, formato HH:MM, <= 21:30)\n- motivo (opcional, max 255 chars)\n\nReglas:\n- horaInicio < horaFin\n- Sin solapamiento con otras reservas\n- Sala debe estar habilitada"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Crear Reserva (Tarde)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Cookie", "value": "next-auth.session-token={{sessionToken}}" }
						],
